// ── SysEx Snapshot — state-change emission (Unit 3.4) ────────────────────────
// g_sysex_dirty is set to 1 by setstate(), undo_pair(), and common_mon_pair()
// whenever Ultra8 lane or monitor state changes. At most one snapshot is emitted
// per audio block, always reflecting the final state after all in-block mutations.
// Resetting the period counter here prevents a redundant heartbeat snapshot from
// firing immediately after a state-change one.
